Interface ICommand

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    FileName, FileSize, FolderFullPath, FolderName, PageSize, PageTitle
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileNameImpl, FileSizeImpl, FolderFullPathImpl, FolderNameImpl, ICommandImpl, PageSizeImpl, PageTitleImpl

    public interface ICommand
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    Interface representing the Commands A representation of the model object 'ICommand'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Result
    • Resource
    • Code Result
    • Name
    • Apply On Folder
    • Apply On File
    • Apply On URI
    See Also:
    tP2_LOG8430Package.getICommand()
